{"type": "article", "id": 4182, "title": "Gathering 餐具系列", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-08T07:41:49Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 20, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606004204cW9xsPN1yrUavdRK.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自香港的设计公司 Saniyo 日前推出了最新的陶瓷餐具系列 Gathering ，在上个月的东京设计周上亮相。正如其名，设计团队希望通过这样一系列餐具，唤起人们珍惜与家人、与朋友在一起吃饭的时光，传达一份分享就是快乐，并且心怀感激的理念。于是，设计团队借由太阳在太阳系种运转，地球公转等天体现象，创作出了这样一套日常生活中的餐具，简洁的线条与形状搭配着明丽的配色，整个系列包含有为拿铁、卡布奇诺与意式浓缩咖啡的专用餐具，以及杯垫、碟子、调味瓶套装等。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004202VCucWZjEJOrpnxHA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606060042023sNejEHdXaTJnPyL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606060042021SvWmDy9uYO3z7Us.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004203JW47pSFKRDIHm8i0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606060042035JoXAxaSbh0iG7rM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}